[brzęczyk]

261
00:15:00,732 --> 00:15:02,566
[ćwierkanie komputera]

262
00:15:02,567 --> 00:15:12,576
[brzęczyk]

263
00:15:12,577 --> 00:15:14,311
[Michael]
Ai...

264
00:15:14,312 --> 00:15:16,747
